text: haey nowpel del yeung ban kamnt sechakdeislab towleu ke( saou lai mean) kmean sanhnhea banhcheak dl puokke( chin) pi moronpheap robsa ke laey tealte dangkouv dei sai chheuchrat robsa ke . haey now pel del sakasap robsa ke ban duol choh puok chin kaban chreab tha brasenbae puokke ban doeng nouv athrkambang noh puokke ka min sthet knong tearounakamm da ameasa noh der
